{"tid":2181451,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有公司強制員工參與病毒檢測","createTime":"2020-08-30T15:10:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T15:10:34.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c71a890e71fa1b6e22238e419963e8a459313fa4","tid":2181451,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T15:10:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/hakukcoohjRS2jLNt_0.0A--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzU5O2g9MjAyO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/News/now.com/TEST-LABOUR-200830-15.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FhakukcoohjRS2jLNt_0.0A--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzU5O2g9MjAyO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2FNews%2Fnow.com%2FTEST-LABOUR-200830-15.jpg&h=6191dc53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有政黨接獲投訴指，有公司強制要求僱員接受病毒檢測。<br />\n<br />\n過去兩周接獲十宗投訴，包括飲食業及院舍的員工，被僱主強迫參與政府為高風險群組提供的免費檢測。有飲食業的員工指，對僱主做法感失望，但在不情願下都交出樣本。<br />\n<br />\n飲食業員工陳先生（化名）：「早上起床收到訊息，叫同事們交深喉唾液測試。我上班，又要送外賣，吃完飯回公司想喝水時，被老闆用粗口罵我，叫我快些做測試。交出樣本後，我又不知你是甚麼用途，為何我要交？不是自願性嗎？我有權不交。為何老闆要迫我們交？」"}]}